	<h4>UCC and FRs&nbsp;</h4>
	<p>S.R. Bommai v. Union of India, the Apex court upheld that religion is the matter of individual faith and cannot be mixed with secular activities. Religion and personal law are different avenues.&nbsp;</p>
	<p>SS khan = <em>Tehzeeb ul akhlaq</em> paper for reforming muslim personal law&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td>NOT favour</td>
	<td>
	<p>suitable conditions exist , trust with minorities first.<br />
	- multi cultural approach pluralism , NE tribes etc&nbsp;</p>
	<p>- Unity does not mean uniformity.<br />
	<br />
	FRs = against 25(freedom of conscience and religion), 26, 29 (right to conserve distinct culture)&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
